extremely frustrating, if you hope to achieve True Wizard status with the 
studs, forget it... you'll die too many times and lose everything you've 
accumulated before you can finish the level. I thought people were being 
dramatic in their reviews, but they are spot on. I am uninstalling the game 
before even finishing it. I used to LOVE playing the first game... this one 
just makes me so disappointed and frustrated. Absolutely not worth it!

both games and would recommend
